extendedInfo.description: Are you feeling bored? We introduce you the new pastime that is going to stir up the way you play with images. This is a puzzle where you can put together even your own photos. Besides that, we also propose you as a challenge to organize some images that come in our application.This is ideal for playing if:You are a student and you are waiting for someone still answering the test. You are about to take the busYou are a business person and you are waiting for a meeting to start. You are stock into traffic.You are waiting to pay your grocery you are waiting for your flight in the waiting room.For this and some much more you will feel amuse while putting together this puzzle pieces of very fun images. Besides now you can organize your own pictures. If you are far away from home you could try to make a puzzle of your family pictures.Characteristics:-Import photos from your image gallery for playing.-Animals and natural scenes awesome images.-You can restore a game after leaving it.-Totally free.-Updates.Stop thinking about it, download this game, is 100% free.
